data.text:
Spain, Cantos populares de Espana. Popular songs of Spain. Good recording. Song list from the Box lid is in the Cobos folder. Julian Grimao, Hermano. 1. Coplas; 2. Los Dos Gallos; 3. Paloma de Paz. Side two songs of Nicaragua is not recorded in the CD. Cobos folder includes lyrics and song texts for the three pieces and also a poem by Grimao., Box: 9, CD: MUS 144. UNM Center for Southwest Research & Special Collections.
